ride.description: Follow the coast as you ride along the magnificent Clarence Drive. You’ll ride from the naval town of Gordon’s Bay to the windswept hamlet of Rooi-Els, and at times will be so close to the water, you can almost touch it!
ride.title: 30 min South Africa Clarence Drive Ride
